{{For|the Japanese television drama|Shiroi Kyotō}}

'''''The Hospital''''' ({{zh-tpl|t=白色巨塔|p=báisè jù tǎ|l=The Great White Tower}}),  is a [[Taiwanese drama]] produced by the group Yang Ming Production.  The series, with thirty-nine 60-minute episodes (including commericials) made its début on [[August 15|15 August]] [[2006]] on [[China Television]] (CTV).  Its scenario is an adaptation of the same book written by Taiwanese author [[Hou Wen Yong]] (侯文詠).

